<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" version="2.0"><channel><title>刘小斌的强迫症治愈之路</title><link>https://xiaobinliu.github.io/ocd</link><description>详细介绍我是如何被强迫症击中和30多年的抗争之路以及我的办法和心得体会</description><copyright>刘小斌的强迫症治愈之路</copyright><docs>http://www.rssboard.org/rss-specification</docs><generator>python-feedgen</generator><image><url>https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1660130?v=4</url><title>avatar</title><link>https://xiaobinliu.github.io/ocd</link></image><lastBuildDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 00:15:29 +0000</lastBuildDate><managingEditor>刘小斌的强迫症治愈之路</managingEditor><ttl>60</ttl><webMaster>刘小斌的强迫症治愈之路</webMaster><item><title>2023年6月28日，接着思考和沟通</title><link>https://xiaobinliu.github.io/ocd/post/2023-nian-6-yue-28-ri-%EF%BC%8C-jie-zhao-si-kao-he-gou-tong.html</link><description>这几天，我可以通过摄像头知道蕙宇回家，做作业，玩游戏，所以基本上能避开吴艳芹。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">https://xiaobinliu.github.io/ocd/post/2023-nian-6-yue-28-ri-%EF%BC%8C-jie-zhao-si-kao-he-gou-tong.html</guid><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 00:15:04 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>2023年6月我的思维</title><link>https://xiaobinliu.github.io/ocd/post/2023-nian-6-yue-wo-de-si-wei.html</link><description>30多年来，我用笑容和强迫掩盖了我极大的痛苦，读三次高中是痛苦的；被我父亲不停的逼迫灌输是痛苦的，尤其是现在知道他自己也没那么优秀；被艳芹不停的逼迫赚钱是痛苦的，尤其是我本没有为她赚钱的责任；我承受的所有的痛苦，其实都是我父亲和艳芹自己的痛苦，我父亲和艳芹有自己的欲望和自己的无能，都想通过我得到满足和释放。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">https://xiaobinliu.github.io/ocd/post/2023-nian-6-yue-wo-de-si-wei.html</guid><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 00:05:04 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>2024年了！我继续思考，深入挖掘思维</title><link>https://xiaobinliu.github.io/ocd/post/2024-nian-le-%EF%BC%81-wo-ji-xu-si-kao-%EF%BC%8C-shen-ru-wa-jue-si-wei.html</link><description>我对我的强迫症有了新发现，不得不说，不说出来我就太冤太悲苦了。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">https://xiaobinliu.github.io/ocd/post/2024-nian-le-%EF%BC%81-wo-ji-xu-si-kao-%EF%BC%8C-shen-ru-wa-jue-si-wei.html</guid><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 23:50:46 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>2024年了，我还是没好，急，和爸爸继续沟通，转变他的看法，减轻我的压力</title><link>https://xiaobinliu.github.io/ocd/post/2024-nian-le-%EF%BC%8C-wo-huan-shi-mei-hao-%EF%BC%8C-ji-%EF%BC%8C-he-ba-ba-ji-xu-gou-tong-%EF%BC%8C-zhuan-bian-ta-de-kan-fa-%EF%BC%8C-jian-qing-wo-de-ya-li.html</link><description>我还是觉得太荒唐了，我治疗我这个病，走了太多弯路，第一个弯路是你们没有一个人配合我治疗，老刘是逃避的，艳芹是敌对的。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">https://xiaobinliu.github.io/ocd/post/2024-nian-le-%EF%BC%8C-wo-huan-shi-mei-hao-%EF%BC%8C-ji-%EF%BC%8C-he-ba-ba-ji-xu-gou-tong-%EF%BC%8C-zhuan-bian-ta-de-kan-fa-%EF%BC%8C-jian-qing-wo-de-ya-li.html</guid><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 23:47:36 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>为了抗争，和学校沟通后，我用孩子的角度写了一篇文章，试图和孩子传达爸爸生病的实情</title><link>https://xiaobinliu.github.io/ocd/post/wei-le-kang-zheng-%EF%BC%8C-he-xue-xiao-gou-tong-hou-%EF%BC%8C-wo-yong-hai-zi-de-jiao-du-xie-le-yi-pian-wen-zhang-%EF%BC%8C-shi-tu-he-hai-zi-chuan-da-ba-ba-sheng-bing-de-shi-qing.html</link><description>我的爸爸，我的爸爸生病在家，躺在房间里睡觉，已经有快两年时间了，我没看过妈妈做饭给他吃，也没看过妈妈带他去医院看过病。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">https://xiaobinliu.github.io/ocd/post/wei-le-kang-zheng-%EF%BC%8C-he-xue-xiao-gou-tong-hou-%EF%BC%8C-wo-yong-hai-zi-de-jiao-du-xie-le-yi-pian-wen-zhang-%EF%BC%8C-shi-tu-he-hai-zi-chuan-da-ba-ba-sheng-bing-de-shi-qing.html</guid><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 23:36:17 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>为了抗争，我试图和孩子学校沟通</title><link>https://xiaobinliu.github.io/ocd/post/wei-le-kang-zheng-%EF%BC%8C-wo-shi-tu-he-hai-zi-xue-xiao-gou-tong.html</link><description>我和我的孩子刘蕙宇都正在遭受来自妈妈的家庭暴力。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">https://xiaobinliu.github.io/ocd/post/wei-le-kang-zheng-%EF%BC%8C-wo-shi-tu-he-hai-zi-xue-xiao-gou-tong.html</guid><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 23:33:03 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>为了抗争，我试图和孩子学校的沟通</title><link>https://xiaobinliu.github.io/ocd/post/wei-le-kang-zheng-%EF%BC%8C-wo-shi-tu-he-hai-zi-xue-xiao-de-gou-tong.html</link><description>---。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">https://xiaobinliu.github.io/ocd/post/wei-le-kang-zheng-%EF%BC%8C-wo-shi-tu-he-hai-zi-xue-xiao-de-gou-tong.html</guid><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 23:29:53 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>2023年我和我父亲的沟通</title><link>https://xiaobinliu.github.io/ocd/post/2023-nian-wo-he-wo-fu-qin-de-gou-tong.html</link><description>有一件事情，一直没说清楚，我的说法是因为你暴力虐待我，造成了三十多年好不了强迫症，造成了十几年无法工作的后果，而且灾难还在继续。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">https://xiaobinliu.github.io/ocd/post/2023-nian-wo-he-wo-fu-qin-de-gou-tong.html</guid><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 23:26:51 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>2023年1月9日我和我父亲的沟通</title><link>https://xiaobinliu.github.io/ocd/post/2023-nian-1-yue-9-ri-wo-he-wo-fu-qin-de-gou-tong.html</link><description>刘小斌 专治野猴:&#13;
领了钱，谢谢，这几天和你沟通，好像你觉得我在2009年之前是没什么强迫症的，你以前也反复流露出这个想法，比如说你说过我，“你能考上大学，你能到上海工作，哪有什么强迫症啊”。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">https://xiaobinliu.github.io/ocd/post/2023-nian-1-yue-9-ri-wo-he-wo-fu-qin-de-gou-tong.html</guid><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 23:21:04 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>2023年10月左右，我已经闭门不出快两年了，我和我家人的沟通。</title><link>https://xiaobinliu.github.io/ocd/post/2023-nian-10-yue-zuo-you-%EF%BC%8C-wo-yi-jing-bi-men-bu-chu-kuai-liang-nian-le-%EF%BC%8C-wo-he-wo-jia-ren-de-gou-tong-%E3%80%82.html</link><description>刘小斌 专治野猴&#13;
