出门在外，手里有手机，回家手机，身份证，钥匙，都在，不用任何焦虑担忧&#13;
断绝任何怀疑心理，比如断绝怀疑一张卡是两张卡&#13;
手机，身份证，三张交通卡&#13;
一手手机，一手身份证，请坚信&#13;
手机，钥匙。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">https://xiaobinliu.github.io/ocd/post/wei-le-dui-kang-qiang-po-%EF%BC%8C-wo-ri-chang-xu-yao-xie-xia-lai-ti-xing-zi-ji-de-hua-%EF%BC%8C-ke-yi-bang-zhu-wo-que-ren.html</guid><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 22:26:11 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>hello2</title><link>https://xiaobinliu.github.io/ocd/post/hello2.html</link><description>hello2 gmeek。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">https://xiaobinliu.github.io/ocd/post/hello2.html</guid><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 13:16:51 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>hello </title><link>https://xiaobinliu.github.io/ocd/post/hello%20.html</link><description>hello gmeek。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">https://xiaobinliu.github.io/ocd/post/hello%20.html</guid><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 13:11:59 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>